      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation or GCI analysis on at least three mesh levels for the hemolysis QoI at all five operating points.",
      "rationale": "GCI analysis was performed at one operating point on two mesh levels only. Extrapolation to the remaining four operating points was not conducted. Achieved level 2."
