      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments performed on the same pump geometry and at COU operating conditions; patient blood analogue fluid used.",
      "rationale": "Validation used a scaled acrylic model and bovine blood rather than the device geometry and a clinical blood analogue. Geometric and fluid differences reduce relevance. Achieved level 2."
