      "acceptanceCriteria": "Monte Carlo UQ on all uncertain input parameters with probability distributions justified by measurement data.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ was initiated but input probability distributions for viscosity and red-cell fragility were assumed uniform without experimental justification. Factor not fully assessed."
